      • MAX_PROCESSES_SUPPORTED

        public static final int MAX_PROCESSES_SUPPORTED
        The maximum amount of processes to support. The Windows API makes no guarantees about this, but faux-empirical testing shows that if you have 65536 processes running simultaneously, you've never even heard of Lacuna.
